# VoiceVault - Voice-Autonomous DeFi Platform

This is a voice-activated DeFi platform being built for the LabLab.ai AI Agents + Arc & USDC hackathon (Oct 27 - Nov 8, 2025).

## Architecture

**Frontend**: Next.js 16 (React 19) with TypeScript, Tailwind CSS, Framer Motion
- Location: `voice-vault/` directory
- Main pages: `app/page.tsx` (dashboard)
- Components: `components/voice-assistant.tsx`, `components/portfolio-overview.tsx`, etc.

**Backend**: FastAPI (Python) - to be created
- Will use OpenAI Agents SDK for multi-agent orchestration
- Integration with Circle User Controlled Wallets SDK
- ElevenLabs for voice STT/TTS
- MongoDB for portfolio & transaction storage
- Arc blockchain via ethers.js

**Key Components**:
- [Voice Assistant](mdc:components/voice-assistant.tsx) - Main voice interface
- [Portfolio Overview](mdc:components/portfolio-overview.tsx) - Portfolio visualization
- [Transaction History](mdc:components/transaction-history.tsx) - Transaction display
- [Plan](mdc:plan.md) - Project roadmap and requirements

## Core Flow
User Voice → ElevenLabs STT → Agents (Planner, Risk, Executor, Auditor) → Circle API → Arc Blockchain → Response

